{"word":"Heman","slug":"heman","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Heman</b> <a href=\"#/H1968\">H1968</a> <br/> 1. A man noted for wisdom, to whom Solomon is compared<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=31'>1Ki 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=6'>1Ch 2:6</a><br/> 2. &#187;The singer&#171; :<br/> - A chief Levite, and musician<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=33'>1Ch 6:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=17'>1Ch 15:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=41'>1Ch 16:41</a> <br/> - The king's seer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=5'>1Ch 25:5</a> <br/> - His sons and daughters temple musicians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=33'>1Ch 6:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=6'>1Ch 25:6</a> <br/> - &#187;Maschil of,&#171; title of Psalm 88<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=88&verse=1'>Psa 88:1</a> "}]}